{"tid":608810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷、葡萄牙友誼賽大敗，係佢地世界盃決賽會碰頭嘅先兆","createTime":"2018-03-28T12:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T09:14:13.000Z","uid":28938,"like":33,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"09c4e852dc477eb12a21b6caf539c6a19f9b6047","tid":608810,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"1.歷史話俾我地知，世界盃決賽周前友賽表現唔好嘅球隊，往往入左決賽周就會有好嘅表現，98年法國、02年德國、06年意粉、10年荷蘭、14年巴西。<br />\n<br />\n2. 好多人以為世界盃係體育盛事，但其實佢都係商業活動。點樣吸引最多人關注世界盃？就係醞釀一場夢幻決賽，美斯對C朗！兩大球王終極之戰，廣告費、轉播收益真係天文數字。國際足協實會幫手<br />\n<br />\n3. 近幾屆世界盃決賽多數南美洲對歐洲國家，決賽阿根廷對葡萄牙，非常合理。<br />\n<br />\n立此post為證，6月開嚟見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d12870107329c7f91cffc833bf0f3b256bed63","tid":608810,"uid":54884,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"提子有咩可能入到"},{"pid":"00e42d1698a3bb9c2306074519daa7a8bc320427","tid":608810,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3348c8b1952656a85c293f3121a53e495a619a10","tid":608810,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"e953e8074a60e1a87e53bf4c0740879a763c5c32","tid":608810,"uid":25267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"幾時有9UP 報專訪睇呀"},{"pid":"9814cbcfd63749dd335833ee5b13ddd57310249f","tid":608810,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"係都幾好睇"},{"pid":"ffabe26c9da29b6abfe9112ef67485ffd4ea3c7c","tid":608810,"uid":169381,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"